00:49:36.190 --> 00:49:38.320
I am -- this was
the 2009 festival,

00:49:38.320 --> 00:49:41.000
the 50th anniversary festival.

00:49:41.000 --> 00:49:44.430
George Wein had sold the
-- after his wife died,

00:49:44.430 --> 00:49:49.780
George Wein sold his
operations to a startup company

00:49:49.780 --> 00:49:53.500
who lasted a couple years before
they went completely broke.

00:49:53.500 --> 00:49:56.230
And with three months
until the 50th anniversary

00:49:56.230 --> 00:49:59.550
of the Newport Folk Festival,
there was no festival.

00:49:59.550 --> 00:50:01.670
So they had to bang up
something very quickly

00:50:01.670 --> 00:50:03.200
without a lot of money.

00:50:03.200 --> 00:50:08.090
And Colin Meloy of the
Decembrists told me

00:50:08.090 --> 00:50:12.720
that he had been told, you know,
his agent told him, "We don't --

00:50:12.720 --> 00:50:14.520
we have no idea whether
they're going

00:50:14.520 --> 00:50:15.860
to actually be able to pay you."

00:50:15.860 --> 00:50:18.380
And he said, "You know,
I don't actually care."

00:50:18.380 --> 00:50:23.410
The point was to celebrate the
Newport Festival and that's

00:50:23.410 --> 00:50:26.260
when a lot of people realized --

00:50:26.260 --> 00:50:30.920
found out how important that
festival had been to a lot

00:50:30.920 --> 00:50:33.740
of people who are
still alive and kicking

00:50:33.740 --> 00:50:36.420
and making new music today.

00:50:36.420 --> 00:50:37.750
A lot of people -- a lot

00:50:37.750 --> 00:50:41.540
of young people who
are still active.

00:50:41.540 --> 00:50:43.710
And, you know, they may be
talking about, you know,

00:50:43.710 --> 00:50:48.660
the '80s festival and, you know,
they sort of know the history

00:50:48.660 --> 00:50:53.520
of the '60s festival and in a
way what the festival did was

00:50:53.520 --> 00:50:56.890
turn that history from sort
of an albatross into a --

00:50:56.890 --> 00:50:58.960
into something that
they celebrate

00:50:58.960 --> 00:51:01.200
and that they recreate.

00:51:01.200 --> 00:51:03.760
